      <h4>Background</h4>
      <p>IDH - The sustainable trade initiative, is based in Amsterdam and aims to improve the economic, social and environmental sustainability of production systems in developing countries, focusing on internationally traded commodities. <br><br>

  I have the great opportunity to be <span class="currently">currently</span> working with them as freelance UX researcher. We are conducting a series of analysis on the website and their users via interviews and usability testing, in order to optimize the website and better serve IDH's business objectives.
  <br><br>
  It is a great company. You might want to discover <a class="idhlink" href="https://www.idhsustainabletrade.com/" target="_blank">them.</a>
  </p>
